I"<p>Mário Espada was born in Lisbon in 1995. He studied piano at the Gregorian Institute of Lisbon. In 2010 he joined the António Arroio Artistic School and continued his film studies at E.S.T.C., where he specialized in Editing. Since 2018 Espada works at Kintop as an editor [Rising Sun Blues (2022), Renata Ferraz; Journey to the Sun (2021), Ansgar Schaefer and Susana de Sousa Dias (IDFA)]. Other editing works include Paradise (2021), by Sérgio Tréfaut and Ciguatera (2022), by Diana Policarpo (Venice Biennale).</p>
